#: ../../en/deployment.rst:2
msgid "Local SFT and vLLM Deployment"
msgstr "本地 SFT 与 vLLM 部署"

#: ../../en/deployment.rst:4
msgid "AnnaAgent can use base models only, but the paper system also uses SFT modules for emotion inference and chief-complaint chain generation. This page explains how to download released assets and deploy local vLLM services."
msgstr "AnnaAgent 可以只使用 base model，但论文系统还包含情绪推断和主诉链生成 SFT 模块。本页说明如何下载资产并在 GPU 机器上部署本地 vLLM 服务。"

#: ../../en/deployment.rst:9
msgid "When to Use This Path"
msgstr "什么时候需要本路径"

#: ../../en/deployment.rst:11
msgid "Use local deployment when:"
msgstr "适合以下情况："

#: ../../en/deployment.rst:13
msgid "You have a Linux GPU machine or cluster node."
msgstr "你有 Linux GPU 机器或集群节点。"

#: ../../en/deployment.rst:14
msgid "You want AnnaAgent to start OpenAI-compatible SFT endpoints for you."
msgstr "你希望 AnnaAgent 自动启动 OpenAI-compatible SFT endpoint。"

#: ../../en/deployment.rst:15
msgid "You want reproducible service logs and workspace-managed endpoint settings."
msgstr "你希望部署日志、PID 和 endpoint 配置都由 workspace 管理。"

#: ../../en/deployment.rst:17
msgid "Stay on base model mode when you only need to run a quick example or do not have GPU access."
msgstr "如果只是快速跑样例，或者没有 GPU，继续使用 base model 模式即可。"

#: ../../en/deployment.rst:21
msgid "Create the Deploy Environment"
msgstr "创建部署环境"

#: ../../en/deployment.rst:23
msgid "The recommended setup keeps the lightweight ``anna`` CLI separate from the heavy vLLM runtime environment."
msgstr "推荐将轻量 ``anna`` CLI 和较重的 vLLM runtime 隔离："

#: ../../en/deployment.rst:34
msgid "The deploy environment is stored at ``anna-workspace/.anna-deploy-venv``. When it exists, ``anna models deploy`` automatically uses the vLLM executable inside that environment."
msgstr "部署环境位于 ``anna-workspace/.anna-deploy-venv``。存在该环境时，``anna models deploy`` 会优先使用其中的 vLLM。"

#: ../../en/deployment.rst:39
msgid "Download Released Assets"
msgstr "下载释放资产"

#: ../../en/deployment.rst:46
msgid "The default paper preset includes the emotion inference SFT model, the chief complaint chain SFT model, and released synthetic data resources."
msgstr "默认 paper preset 包括 emotion SFT、chief complaint chain SFT 和合成数据资源。"

#: ../../en/deployment.rst:50
msgid "Deploy Services"
msgstr "启动服务"

#: ../../en/deployment.rst:52
msgid "Deploy the complaint model:"
msgstr "部署 complaint 模型："

#: ../../en/deployment.rst:59
msgid "Deploy the emotion model:"
msgstr "部署 emotion 模型："

#: ../../en/deployment.rst:66
msgid "If you have one GPU, deploy one target at a time or lower memory utilization."
msgstr "如果只有一张 GPU，请分开部署或降低显存使用率。"

#: ../../en/deployment.rst:69
msgid "What the CLI Checks"
msgstr "CLI 会检查什么"

#: ../../en/deployment.rst:71
msgid "Before starting vLLM, AnnaAgent checks:"
msgstr "启动 vLLM 前，AnnaAgent 会检查："

#: ../../en/deployment.rst:73
msgid "``nvidia-smi`` availability."
msgstr "``nvidia-smi`` 是否可用。"

#: ../../en/deployment.rst:74
msgid "Whether the requested GPU ID exists."
msgstr "指定 GPU ID 是否存在。"

#: ../../en/deployment.rst:75
msgid "Free GPU memory and the requested vLLM memory cap."
msgstr "剩余显存和 vLLM 显存上限。"

#: ../../en/deployment.rst:76
msgid "CUDA toolkit visibility through ``--cuda-home``, ``CUDA_HOME``, ``PATH``, common CUDA roots, or cluster modules."
msgstr "CUDA toolkit 是否能从 ``--cuda-home``、``CUDA_HOME``、``PATH``、常见 CUDA root 或集群 module 中找到。"

#: ../../en/deployment.rst:77
msgid "``ninja`` availability for FlashInfer JIT builds."
msgstr "FlashInfer JIT 所需的 ``ninja`` 是否可用。"

#: ../../en/deployment.rst:79
msgid "If a workspace deploy environment is missing ``ninja``, AnnaAgent installs it into that environment before starting vLLM. CUDA module loading affects only the vLLM child process and does not modify the user's shell."
msgstr "如果 workspace 部署环境缺少 ``ninja``，AnnaAgent 会在启动 vLLM 前自动安装。自动 CUDA module 加载只影响 vLLM 子进程，不会污染用户 shell。"

#: ../../en/deployment.rst:84
msgid "Custom CUDA or vLLM Paths"
msgstr "自定义 CUDA 或 vLLM 路径"

#: ../../en/deployment.rst:86
msgid "Use ``--cuda-home`` only when CUDA is installed in a custom location:"
msgstr "只有 CUDA 安装在特殊位置时才需要 ``--cuda-home``："

#: ../../en/deployment.rst:93
msgid "Use ``--vllm-command`` when your cluster already provides vLLM:"
msgstr "如果集群已经提供 vLLM："

#: ../../en/deployment.rst:101
msgid "Failure Behavior"
msgstr "失败行为"

#: ../../en/deployment.rst:103
msgid "If startup fails or the readiness check times out, AnnaAgent prints the service log tail and does not write a bad endpoint into ``settings.yaml``. Logs and PIDs are stored under ``logs/services/`` and ``runs/services/`` inside the workspace."
msgstr "如果服务启动失败或 readiness 超时，AnnaAgent 会打印服务日志尾部，并且不会把坏 endpoint 写入 ``settings.yaml``。日志和 PID 位于 workspace 的 ``logs/services/`` 与 ``runs/services/``。"

#: ../../en/deployment.rst:107
msgid "Check the status after deployment:"
msgstr "查看状态："
